{"tid":2097572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"羅庭德：因有老師與確診者共處 上水鳳溪創新小學今日緊急停課","createTime":"2020-07-07T02:41:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T05:09:31.000Z","uid":22556,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6a4e4a89715067140d77015304421d4a4344123e","tid":2097572,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T02:41:17.000Z","msg":"【上水鳳溪創新小學今日停課】<br />\n<br />\n北區區議會開會中<br />\n已向教育局官員Fact Check<br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n校方剛接獲通知，本校一名老師上周六與一位剛確診新冠肺炎患者曾短暫共處，正待衛生署檢測。老師已即時通知校方作出緊急應變，校方現作出以下安排：<br />\n<br />\n1. 由於老師仍未待進行測試，待有消息便即時通知校方有關檢測結果。<br />\n<br />\n2. 學校為謹慎處理，故安排今天(7/7)停課一天，包括zoom視訊課堂，唯六年級升中放榜工作仍如期舉行。<br />\n<br />\n3. 校舍今天將繼續開放，照顧有需要回校的學生，但家長必須為學生做足防疫措施。<br />\n<br />\n4. 校舍將會全面消毒，亦已促請校巴公司再次全面消毒。<br />\n<br />\n5. 請各位密切留意子女身體狀況，如有不適請立即求醫及與校方聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n惟鑑於尚未進行化驗，此階段校方不宜透露老師姓名。學校會繼續密切留意有關情況，如有最新消息將盡快通知大家。<br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/103142554391351/posts/303162984389306/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F103142554391351%2Fposts%2F303162984389306%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=uYDAXyhVPN7xTSuHIXBXEnjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=82a12e76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/103142554391351/posts/303162984389306/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"43aecd1ae53900c5bf5f08f45cf09cf6c6707ded","tid":2097572,"uid":280475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T02:42:48.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"2db90a332c265259a3fe2a2348000303f7497246","tid":2097572,"uid":280475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T02:43:04.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"27329288d630ce1ad66e3e6c95fc14536381f677","tid":2097572,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T02:44:34.000Z","msg":"第二波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e0e5f12d04cac5b0637a43e13018af2df735d32","tid":2097572,"uid":53003,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T02:55:04.000Z","msg":"無啦啦又會有咁多人感染<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又要收緊限聚令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95f6a9537e7aeda3adfcbfcdaecf17d1081858e8","tid":2097572,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:51:08.000Z","msg":"加甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140c717acc02141fa51c324d44a649f484c0a030","tid":2097572,"uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:52:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hd0gJr7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhd0gJr7.png&h=ecee0ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"423306b83f04d84350ba221e9224c9706c17def0","tid":2097572,"uid":5373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:57:32.000Z","msg":"係咪跨境學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93de2d5bc030da524c76dd712cb792294de337c","tid":2097572,"uid":247184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:59:56.000Z","msg":"唔巧B愧田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43cd39ed4251e3fa6db79b5c4139deff1885bb10","tid":2097572,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T05:09:31.000Z","msg":"共處<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}